# Per-item knowledge-graph JSON (~6,000 files, ~188 MB) is regenerated in-Omeka
# via the admin "Regenerate now" job — not committed. The front-end falls back to
# the live REST API until it has been generated in the container.
asset/data/knowledge-graphs/

# Per-item-set photo-gallery JSON is install-specific (media storage hashes) and
# regenerated in-Omeka by the same job. The Photo Browsing block falls back to
# live API resolution until it has been generated.
asset/data/photo-galleries/
